+ lam tiep phan xoa bang javaScript(Chu y ',"), da xoa duoc trong database.
+ demo truyen tham so vao js bang HTML: <td><a href="javascript:xoaKhachHang('${kh.maKH}')">Xoa</a></td>

Note cho Spring security:
- khong co <servlet> wrap <filter>
- query user instead of member
- khai bao cac trang dang nhap, dang xuat, dang ky, role, phuong thuc dang nhap, dang xuat, lop userService<authentication-provider>userService<> 
trong spring-security.xml, spring se tu thuc hien xet duyet dang nhap.
- khai bao duong dan theo role: /admin/* thi admin se duoc vao trang. /user/* thi user duoc xem trang, do spring-security quan ly.
- chinh sua role trong database/sql.
